#summary This is the Example 3

= Search all human proteins are linked to all elements on the Ontology list =

On this example the [DesktopTool Desktop Tool] [SearchTab Search Tab], [SQLEditor SQL Editor Tab] and the [JavaAPI Java API] will be used to search the all human proteins which are linked to all elements on the Ontology list.

The ontology list will be integrated by the glycoprotein metabolic process (GO:0009100) and the glycoprotein biosynthetic process (GO:0009101).
